metadata.name: MY NAME IS MINT
metadata.description:
Based on real-life, this is the first digital unique, original artwork of 150 artworks series inspired by a female rescue dog.  
Her body is made of colorful tears representing both her sad life and story, her sweetness, good energy, and life willpower. 
She is depicted as her starts, in a grayish place, meaning a place with no light of care and love. 

Crown Dogs Mint collection is dedicated to her with much love and hopes that your support will help keep rescuing more furry wagging tales friends.
